 out there you feel something touch you. Or is that your imagination. <br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1492287649ra/22502455.gif" alt=" " class="gr-hostedUserImg" loading="lazy"><br><br>Then of course you freak out some more. People, I would never exist for more than a second in this world! <br><br>I liked some of the people Malorie was living with and they were doing okay, until . . . that one day they let the wrong person in. . . sigh. . . . . . <br><br>I mean you have a nice little set up with your dogs and birds and food and then, BAM! Anyhoo, none of that happens until later on during a very crazy night. That's all I'm saying. <br><br>Malorie lives in a house for 4 years. She raises children. Then what happens? Read the book and find out =)<br><br>MY BLOG: <a href="http://melissa413readsalot.blogspot.com/2017/04/bird-box-by-josh-malerman.html" rel="nofollow noopener">Melissa Martin's Reading List</a><br><br>Mel 🖤🐶🐺🐾</span></div></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"><ul class="CollapsableList"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17438949?shelf=horror-gothic-etc" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">horror-gothic-etc</span></a> <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17438949?shelf=own" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">own</span></a></ul></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">372 likes</span></button></div><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">53 comments</span></button></div></div><div data-testid="actions"><div class="SocialFooter__action"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" c